                                <p>
                                <div class="d-inline-block topic">
                                    <h2> Parents should not force their child to choose career due to the following
                                        reasons-</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-inline-block topic">
                                    <h4>1. Only once in a lifetime a person decides his career.</h4>
                                </div>
                                <p>Career is important and impacts one's entire future.we have seen many cases in which
                                    the child chooses career forced by parents and ends up being depressed.</p>
                                <div class="d-inline-block topic">
                                    <h4>2. Everyone is blessed and unique</h4>
                                </div>
                                <p>It is rightly said "EVERYBODY IS GENIUS.BUT IF YOU JUDGE A FISH BY ITS ABILITY TO
                                    CLIMB THE TREE,IT WILL LIVE ITS WHOLE LIFE BELIEVING THAT IT IS STUPID". </p>
                                <p>Some kids are good at art and some are good at mathematics. We cannot force an Art
                                    Loving child to study mathematics.</p>


